{"data_series_issue_identification_fra": "1.0", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\\u00e9o", "title_fra": "CanMatrix - Pr\u00eat \u00e0 imprimer - 013K13", "data_series_issue_identification": "1.0", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "CanMatrix - Pr\u00eat \u00e0 imprimer", "spatial_representation_type": "Map Digital | Carte num\u00e9rique", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "As Needed | Au besoin", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Les fichiers CanMatrix - Pr\u00eat \u00e0 imprimer ont \u00e9t\u00e9 produits \u00e0 partir des cartes topographiques publi\u00e9es par le Gouvernement du Canada. Ces fichiers sont bas\u00e9s sur le Syst\u00e8me national de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence cartographique (SNRC) et disponibles aux \u00e9chelles de 1/50 000 et 1/250 000. Chaque fichier ou jeu de donn\u00e9es CanMatrix - Pr\u00eat \u00e0 imprimer contient l'ensemble de l'information figurant au recto de la carte topographique. Cela comprend l'information topographique incluse \u00e0 l'int\u00e9rieur de l'orle cartographique de m\u00eame que l'habillage de la carte, soit l'information situ\u00e9e en p\u00e9riph\u00e9rie de l'orle cartographique.  Les donn\u00e9es contenues dans ce fichier CanMatrix - Pr\u00eat \u00e0 imprimer proviennent du balayage d'une carte topographique papier monochrome (noir et blanc).  Suite au balayage initial de la carte papier, ce fichier a \u00e9t\u00e9 inspect\u00e9 et class\u00e9 \" Provisoire\". Ce fichier inclut un filigrane \"Impression provisoire\" au bas du coin inf\u00e9rieur gauche de la carte. La qualit\u00e9 des impressions provisoire varie grandement. Un certain nombre d'op\u00e9rations de nettoyage, d\u00e9coupage, mise \u00e0 l'\u00e9chelle et ajustement des tons et couleurs peuvent \u00eatre n\u00e9cessaires afin d'am\u00e9liorer la qualit\u00e9 de l'impression.", "presentation_form": "Map Digital | Carte num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[-62, 54.75], [-62, 55], [-61.5, 55], [-61.5, 54.75], [-62, 54.75]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/canmatrix2/50k_pdf/013/k/canmatrix2_013k13_pdf.zip", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "PDF"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/canmatrix2/50k_pdf/013/k/canmatrix2_013k13_pdf.zip", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "PDF"}, {"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/canmatrix2/50k_tif/013/k/canmatrix2_013k13_tif.zip", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "TIFF"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/canmatrix2/50k_tif/013/k/canmatrix2_013k13_tif.zip", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "TIFF"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "Imagery Base Maps Earth Cover  Imagerie carte de base couverture terrestre", "tags": [{"name": "CANMATRIX2013K131.0  CANMATRIX2013K131.0"}, {"name": "Earth Science  Sciences de la Terre"}, {"name": "013K13  013K13"}], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "2010-11-02", "time_period_coverage_start": "1987", "data_series_name": "CanMatrix - Print Ready", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "1987", "name": "0013690f-1dd8-4f35-865c-0b7833c76b20", "language": "", "url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/0013690f-1dd8-4f35-865c-0b7833c76b20.html", "notes": "CanMatrix - Print Ready files were produced from topographic maps published by the Government of Canada, and correspond to the National Topographic System (NTS) grid at 1:50 000 and 1:250 000 scales. Each CanMatrix - Print Ready file or dataset contains all of the information shown on the front of the topographic map, including the topographic information within the neatline of the map, and the information in the border of the map outside of the neatline.  This CanMatrix - Print Ready file was produced by scanning a monochrome (black and white) paper topographic map.  Following initial scanning of the paper map, the digital file was inspected and classified as \"Provisional\". This file includes a \"Provisional Print\" watermark in the bottom left corner of the map. The printing quality of Provisional Prints varies greatly. Varying amounts of cleaning, trimming, scaling, and shade/colour adjustment may be required to improve the print quality.", "title": "CanMatrix - Print Ready - 013K13", "url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/0013690f-1dd8-4f35-865c-0b7833c76b20.html", "department_number": ""}
{"data_series_issue_identification_fra": "N60d19mW104d10m_7", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\\u00e9o", "title_fra": "Base de donn\u00e9es des points d'appui au sol, Canada - N60d19mW104d10m_7", "data_series_issue_identification": "N60d19mW104d10m_7", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "Base de donn\u00e9es des points d'appui au sol, Canada", "spatial_representation_type": "Image Digital | Image num\u00e9rique", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "La Base de donn\u00e9es des points d'appui au sol (BDPAS) est une collection d'orthophotographies (ou chips) destin\u00e9e aux utilisateurs de SIG et de t\u00e9l\u00e9d\u00e9tection. La base de donn\u00e9es fournit une information utile et exacte \u00e9tablie \u00e0 partir de photos a\u00e9riennes corrig\u00e9es. L'utilisateur final peut s'y reporter \u00e0 titre de source de donn\u00e9es fondamentales pour corriger et valider les donn\u00e9es satellitaires, vectorielles et matricielles, pour fins de correction et de mise \u00e0 jour des cartes ainsi que d'analyse, de mod\u00e9lisation et de traitement des images. La BDPAS a d'abord \u00e9t\u00e9 constitu\u00e9e pour suppl\u00e9er au traitement et/ou \u00e0 la correction des donn\u00e9es LANDSAT et SPOT afin d'offrir des produits d'imagerie satellitaire \u00e0 valeur ajout\u00e9e. G\u00e9ogratis offre maintenant \u00e0 l'utilisateur final la possibilit\u00e9 d'acc\u00e9der \u00e0 ces donn\u00e9es en ligne de mani\u00e8re efficace et \u00e9conomique.", "presentation_form": "Image Digital | Image num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[60.305315, -104.232777], [60.3239, -104.232341], [60.323683, -104.195682], [60.305099, -104.196139], [60.305315, -104.232777]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W104/N60/N60d19mW104d10m_7.gtif", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "GeoTIFF"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W104/N60/N60d19mW104d10m_7.tfw", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "TIFF World File"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W104/N60/N60d19mW104d10m_7.tif", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "TIFF"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W104/N60/N60d19mW104d10m_7.summary", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "text"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "Location  Localisation", "tags": [{"name": "Geomatics  G\u00e9omatique"}, {"name": "Geographic data  Donn\u00e9es g\u00e9ographiques"}, {"name": "Photography  Photographie"}, {"name": "Aerial photography  Photographie a\u00e9rienne"}, {"name": "Imagery and Basemaps  Imagerie et carte de base"}, {"name": "GCP  BDPC"}, {"name": "Air photo  Photo a\u00e9rienne"}, {"name": "Ground Control Points  Points dappui au sol"}, {"name": "NTS 75A8  SNRC 75A8"}], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "1980-08-13", "time_period_coverage_start": "", "data_series_name": "Ground Control Database, Canada", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "", "name": "0014b7c5-dbec-51b6-9f5a-e3864276de23", "language": "", "url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/0014b7c5-dbec-51b6-9f5a-e3864276de23.html", "notes": "The Ground Control Database (GCDB) is a collection of geo-corrected aerial photo images (or chips) developed for the GIS and remote sensing community. The database provides accurate and useful information obtained from corrected aerial photos. This database can be used by the end-user as a fundamental data source for correction and validation of satellite, vector and raster data, as well as for map correcting and updating, analysis, modeling, and image processing. The GCDB was initially developed to supplement processing and/or correction of LANDSAT and SPOT data for value added satellite imagery products. Now, through GeoGratis, online access to the GCDB is offered as an efficient and cost effective method of delivery to the end-user.", "title": "Ground Control Database, Canada - N60d19mW104d10m_7", "url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/0014b7c5-dbec-51b6-9f5a-e3864276de23.html", "department_number": ""}
